'''悉尼板球場'''（Sydney Cricket Ground，'''SCG'''）是位於[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]][[悉尼|悉尼]]的一座體育場，主要同於舉辦板球賽事。悉尼板球場由悉尼板球場信託運營。除了板球外，悉尼板球場亦舉辦[[聯盟式橄欖球|聯盟式橄欖球]]等體育賽事<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.espn.com.au/rugby/story/_/id/23109528/waratahs-not-inspired-scg-rich-rugby-history-growden|title=Waratahs can't not be inspired by SCG history|work=ESPN.com|access-date=2018-04-26|archive-date=2019-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190510021002/http://www.espn.com.au/rugby/story/_/id/23109528/waratahs-not-inspired-scg-rich-rugby-history-growden|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://austadiums.com/sport/event.php?eventid=20704|title=Super Rugby: Waratahs v Reds {{!}} Austadiums|website=austadiums.com|access-date=2018-04-26|archive-date=2021-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211201050229/https://www.austadiums.com/sport/event.php?eventid=20704|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年，悉尼板球場啟用了新的LED大屏幕<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.austadiums.com/news/news.php?id=621|title=New SCG scoreboard debuts as soccer returns|work=Austadiums|access-date=2018-11-10|archive-date=2019-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421060128/https://www.austadiums.com/news/news.php?id=621|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
